{"consensus_set_id":"s408498","translation_language":"fa","translation_source":{"hid":"408498"},"segments":[{"source_hadith_segment":"« قَالَ اَللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ :   <quranic_text> « وَ لَهُ مَنْ فِي السَّمٰاوٰاتِ وَ الْاَرْضِ وَ مَنْ عِنْدَهُ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الانبياء ۱۹ ] </footnote>   ،  يَعْنِي الْمَلاَئِكَةَ : <quranic_text> « لاٰ يَسْتَكْبِرُونَ عَنْ عِبٰادَتِهِ وَ لاٰ يَسْتَحْسِرُونَ يُسَبِّحُونَ اللَّيْلَ وَ النَّهٰارَ لاٰ يَفْتُرُونَ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الانبياء ۱۹ ] </footnote> ،  وَ قَالَ اللَّهُ تَعَالَي فِي الْمَلاَئِكَةِ :   <quranic_text> « بَلْ عِبٰادٌ مُكْرَمُونَ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الانبياء ۲۶ ] </footnote> <quranic_text> « لاٰ يَسْبِقُونَهُ بِالْقَوْلِ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الانبياء ۲۷ ] </footnote>  اِلَي قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَي :   <quranic_text> « مُشْفِقُونَ » </quranic_text>   <footnote> [ الانبياء ۲۸ ] </footnote>   .","translation_segment":"","segment_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"قال","display":"قَالَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الله","display":"اَللَّهُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"عز","display":"عَزَّ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"جل","display":"جَلَّ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"له","display":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"السماوات","display":"السَّمٰاوٰاتِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"الارض","display":"الْاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"عنده","display":"عِنْدَهُ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"الانبياء","display":"الانبياء"},{"kind":"word","token":"۱۹","display":"۱۹"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"يعني","display":"يَعْنِي"},{"ki